name: Pac-In-Time [GB]
description:
Pac-In-Time is an arcade game developed by Kalisto Entertainment and Kalisto. It came out on 01-01-1994. It was published by MINDSCAPE. The game is rated as "Meh" on RAWG.
You can play Pac-In-Time on SNES, Game Boy, Classic Macintosh and PC.
Frédéric Motte scored the game.
